729837f-b.title: Richmond: Victory Boulevard - Cebra Avenue
729837f-b.text:
Victory Boulevard, north from Cebra Avenue. The thoroughfare bends eastward as it deseends the hill and approaches Avon
Plaoe.
1926
P. L. Sperr

The east side of the Boulevard at Cebra Avenue. These frame houses, the rears of which are shown, front on Rosewood Place.
